notesStmt.note: This seminar discussion takes place in the course of an arts class at an international summer school. S1, the teacher, and her students are discussing a text that the students were asked to read as homework, about the artist Chris Burden and his art installations and actions. S1 guides the discussion and also calls on specific students to give details about various art installations. After they have described four particular pieces of art, S1 invites the students to give their opinions on the artist and what he was trying to achieve with his art, and a lively discussion evolves.

equipment.p: Portable minidisc recorder with electret condenser stereo microphone
